title: High school boys soccer: Lyons Township, Morton, Riverside Brookfield primed for postseason kickoff
text:
Sectional seed: No. 3 
First match: 4:30 p.m. Oct. 21 vs. No. 14 Whitney Young 
Outlook: The Lions are the top seed in their regional and are behind only state powerhouses Hinsdale Central (No. 1) and Morton (No. 2) in the sectional seedings. LT topped Whitney Young 1-0 in the first game of the season and it will look for a similar result in order to reach the regional championship game Oct. 24. If the Lions win the regional, they are likely to draw Morton in the sectional semifinal Oct. 27. 
Morton
